Sangameng Quyngit Aghulisigatat
Quutmiit Ungipaghaat

Ilangani, quyngim nallaamakanga afsengaq.
Afsengaq peghqinghumalghii.

Afsengaam aaptaa, "Quyngiq, navek piiqsin?"

Quyngim akitaa, "Vegaaghmeng meghmeng ivaghiqunga."

Afsengaam pii, "Wiin iighaataghteltung."

"A-aa," aangghaa Quyngim.

"Quneghhnaqunga sivukluten elpek iighi ivaghlleqamken," Afsengaam kayagtaa.

Quyngiq iighyaghtughtuq vegaaghtuqamun.
Taawanginaq sighuneghqek aliituk.

Afsengaam maatghaq naalkaa Quyngiq qayughllak sighuneghqek esghaqek.

Quyngim pii, "Haa, elpegngam iighi ivaghnaqamken."

Quyngiq quneghsan Afsengaq iighyaghtughtuq vegaaghmun.

Quyngim ivaghaa, ivaghaa Afsengaq.

Whavemun kenlanga naalkigataa.
